th a playful yet modern form\n\nSized for children aged 4–8 years\n\nIntegrated steering wheel (non-functional, playful control)\n\nComfortable contoured seat with backrest\n\nBuilt-in footrest\n\nSide guards and lap safety belt\n\nAttachment & Safety Mechanism\n\nClearly visible locking / hooking mechanism connecting the mini car to the trolley\n\nMechanism should look:\n\nStrong\n\nStable\n\nEasy to attach and detach\n\nDesign should ensure:\n\nNo tipping risk\n\nWeight evenly distributed\n\nWheels aligned with trolley movemen","Create a high quality realistic 3D product render of an airport lugga","https://tripo-public.tripo3d.ai/studio/project/73f9cb19-b6de-4f16-9147-5789b18f3fd4/Create-a-high-quality-realistic-3D-product-render-of-an-airport-lugga.webp",[],"realistic","rendering",[266,267],"https://tripo-data.rg1.data.tripo3d.com/tripo-studio/20260212/3cc2c7cc-e508-4b02-8e53-4754756842b2/studio_mesh.webp?Key-Pair-Id=K1676C64NMVM2J&Policy=eyJTdGF0ZW1lbnQiOlt7IlJlc291cmNlIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly90cmlwby1kYXRhLnJnMS5kYXRhLnRyaXBvM2QuY29tL3RyaXBvLXN0dWRpby8yMDI2MDIxMi8zY2MyYzdjYy1lNTA4LTRiMDItOGU1My00NzU0NzU2ODQyYjIvc3R1ZGlvX21lc2gud2VicCIsIkNvbmRpdGlvbiI6eyJEYXRlTGVzc1RoYW4iOnsiQVdTOkVwb2NoVGltZSI6MTc3Mjc1NTIwMH19fV19&Signature=DhXn9vbk8Gc0mzspj~dnRLGXhdyXT4aaAGbAkBet3CotC-krac3P8pr-IrBwehVx3nFyTdbr3yDd0xA3kvjXuuWDXVkoqUHQlgoDVklkXJoSKslENQk5IlJMDjI7-KbtL7AYcnYk~DOMszvtKc8m8aBeNzZA2kEKBE2mkQTy816O5wp-EW~aVGOJYp~-w20m-q4trdo8oJWSg1siUmCT3xjPuXikaYpss53vWIYAItDRTbh4ouPcg9xDQlP89HMzvZBEKvEhWQyT4EE92yyuXYNoNDArsBt0jBwEWqAjysjMht1akC9GeXTeuuN~GjbyykbRRuj4Hp5g-VRZwjb6Mg__","https://tripo-data.rg1.data.tripo3d.com/tripo-studio/20260212/3cc2c7cc-e508-4b02-8e53-4754756842b2/studio_mesh_gray.webp?Key-Pair-Id=K1676C64NMVM2J&Policy=eyJTdGF0ZW1lbnQiOlt7IlJlc291cmNlIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly90cmlwby1kYXRhLnJnMS5kYXRhLnRyaXBvM2QuY29tL3RyaXBvLXN0dWRpby8yMDI2MDIxMi8zY2MyYzdjYy1lNTA4LTRiMDItOGU1My00NzU0NzU2ODQyYjIvc3R1ZGlvX21lc2hfZ3JheS53ZWJwIiwiQ29uZGl0aW9uIjp7IkRhdGVMZXNzVGhhbiI6eyJBV1M6RXBvY2hUaW1lIj