zed":32,"is_pbr":13,"is_hd_textured":13,"is_nexus_mesh":32,"is_nsfw":32,"image_prompt_to_model":281,"is_latest_operator":13},"3cc2c7cc-e508-4b02-8e53-4754756842b2",{"transform_matrix":273,"children_transform_matrix":274,"children_deleted":275,"children_rename":276,"material_factor":277},[],{},[],{},{"metallic":240,"roughness":240},[266,267],1770878960,1770879091,{"prompt":282,"image":206,"style":206,"private":32,"style_image":206,"negative_prompt":4,"quad":32,"smart_poly":32,"face_limit":31,"texture":13,"pbr":13,"texture_quality":161,"texture_alignment":159,"generate_parts":32,"texture_seed":206,"geometry_quality":135,"visibility":70,"sketch_to_render":32,"t_pose":32,"gen_image_model_version":248,"model_version":233},"Create a high-quality, realistic 3D product render of an airport luggage trolley integrated with a detachable mini ride-on car for children.\n\nMain Product Components\n\n1. Airport Luggage Trolley\n\nStandard airport trolley design\n\nMetal tubular frame with matte silver finish\n\nFour smooth-rolling wheels with brakes\n\nFlat luggage platform holding suitcases\n\nErgonomic push handle for adults\n\n2. Mini Ride-On Car (Child Module)\n\nCompact, child-friendly mini car attached to the front of the trolley\n\nSmooth, rounded edges with a playful yet modern form\n\nSized for children aged 4–8 years\n\nIntegrated steering wheel (non-functional, playful control)\n\nComfortable contoured seat with backrest\n\nBuilt-in footrest\n\nSide guards and lap safety belt\n\nAttachment & Safety Mechanism\n\nClearly visible locking / hooking mechanism connecting the mini car to the trolley\n\nMechanism should look:\n\nStrong\n\nStable\n\nEasy to attach and detach\n\nDesign should ensure:\n\nNo tipping risk\n\nWeight evenly distributed\n\nWheels aligned with trolley movement\n\nMaterials & Finish\n\nMini car made of durable molded plastic (ABS-like finish)\n\nSoft-touch seat surface\n\nMetal connectors at attachment points\n\nNon-slip texture on footrest\n\nColor & Aesthetics\n\nChild-friendly color palette:\n\nPrimary body: bright yellow or blue\n\nAccent details in red and white\n\nClean, minimal industrial design\n\nNo sharp corners or exposed fasteners\n\nUser & Scale Reference\n\nInclude a neutral child silhouette sitting in the mini car to show scale\n\nDo not show facial details\n\nShow an adult hand pushing the trolley (optional)\n\nEnvironment\n\nAirport-inspired setting:\n\nSmooth terminal flooring\n\nSubtle signage or glass walls in background\n\nAlternatively, a clean studio background for clarity\n\nCamera & Views\n\nPerspective hero shot showing full product\n\nSide view showing attachment mechanism\n\nFront view focusing on mini car\n\nClose-up of safety and locking system\n\nLighting & Render Style\n\nSoft, realistic lighting\n\nClear shadows for depth\n\nHigh-resolution, photorealistic product visualization\n\nProfessional industrial design render quality\n\nConcept Goal\n\nThe design should clearly communicate how the mini ride-on car transforms long airport walks into a playful, enjoyable experience for children while making travel easier for parents.",{"max_retries":31,"used_retries":31,"remaining_retries":31,"can_retry":32,"can_show_retry":32},{"owner_name":285,"owner_avatar":173,"id":286,"project_name":287,"like_count":31,"collect_count":31,"liked":32,"collected":32,"type":69,"visibility":70,"biz_info":288,"custom_tags":292,"category":224,"style":182,"use_case":183,"is_featured":32,"cover_image":293,"is_nsfw":32,"model_url":296,"point_cloud_model_url":297,"is_owner":32,"operator":298,"retry_info":320},"Anonymous1769644287","9c9bad72-e2a6-425b-9c83-1d0ee92989b5","cartoon robot 3d model",{"description":289,"short_description":290,"display_image":291},"robot character with white torso, dark head, light blue accents, AH on chest, articulated arms, hovering above a pedestal","robot character with white torso dark head light blue accents AH on","https://tripo-public.tripo3d.ai/studio/project/9c9bad72-e2a6-425b-9c